---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="About - TinyKite" 
  description="Learn about TinyKite and our mission to build utility apps that make your life easier."
>
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">About TinyKite</h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
            TinyKite is dedicated to creating simple, fast, and beautiful utility applications that solve real problems.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            We believe that great software doesn't have to be complicated. Our mission is to build 
            tools that are intuitive, efficient, and respectful of your privacy. Every app we create 
            is designed with a single purpose: to make your life easier.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Build</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            At TinyKite, we focus on utility applications that serve specific needs. Whether it's 
            productivity tools, developer utilities, or everyday helpers, each app is crafted with 
            attention to detail and user experience.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Values</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Simplicity:</strong> We believe in clean, intuitive interfaces that anyone can use.</li>
            <li><strong>Performance:</strong> Our apps are built for speed and efficiency.</li>
            <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> Your data is yours. We don't track, sell, or misuse your information.</li>
            <li><strong>Quality:</strong> We take pride in shipping polished, well-tested products.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Get in Touch</h2>
          <p class="mb-4">
            Have questions, feedback, or ideas for new apps? We'd love to hear from you. 
            Check out our <a href="/blog" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark underline">blog</a> for 
            updates, or browse our <a href="/apps" class="text-primary hover:text-primary-dark underline">apps</a> to 
            see what we're building.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .prose {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300;
  }
  
  .prose h2 {
    @apply text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100;
  }
  
  .prose p {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300;
  }
  
  .prose ul li {
    @apply text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300;
  }
  
  .prose strong {
    @apply text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 font-semibold;
  }
</style>
